Helix::Driver::Template::Toolkit, version 0.01
==============================================

The Helix::Driver::Template::Toolkit is a template driver for Helix Framework. 
It is based on famous Template::Toolkit package, that provides a lot of tasty 
functions for separating code and markup.

INSTALLATION

To install the driver type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

To use this driver you must have the following packages installed:

    Template
    Helix

